<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFBFF956754145B45" box="[1078,1094,837,862]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="7.0">7</number>
: 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFB809567540B5B45" box="[1097,1113,837,862]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="6.0">6</number>
: 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFB949567543E5B45" box="[1117,1132,837,862]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="5.0">5</number>
. Mid leg: coxa with some anterior and a strong anterolateral setae; femur with strong anterior preapical seta; tibia with row of 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFAD29548557B5B99" box="[1307,1321,874,898]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="4.0">4</number>
strong ad setae; 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFF1795AC50BE5BBD" box="[222,236,910,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="2.0">2</number>
strong pd setae at 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFE0995AF51985BBD" box="[448,458,909,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFE1C95AF51B65BBD" box="[469,484,909,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="5.0">5</number>
and 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFDD595AC52795BBD" box="[540,555,910,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="2.0">2</number>
/3, 1 strong av seta at 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFCEB95AC53635BBD" box="[802,817,910,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="2.0">2</number>
/ 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFCF295AC531A5BBD" box="[827,840,910,934]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="3.0">3</number>
, and circlet of strong apical setae; relative podomere ratios: 
<number id="352EF86C3E34AD0CFF2D959351575BD1" box="[228,261,945,970]" pageId="3" pageNumber="128" value="67.0">67</number>
